---
const navItems = [
  { label: 'Writing', href: '/writing/' },
  { label: 'Logs', href: '/logs/' },
  { label: 'Projects', href: '/projects/' },
  { label: 'About', href: '/about/' },
  { label: 'GitHub', href: 'https://github.com/sugargeng' },
];
---

<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>sugargeng</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="sugargeng 的公开学习系统，记录 AI 应用、软件工程、项目复盘和长期成长。"
    />
  </head>

  <body>
    <main class="site">
      <header class="nav">
        <a class="brand" href="/">sugargeng</a>

        <nav>
          {navItems.map((item) => (
            <a href={item.href}>{item.label}</a>
          ))}
        </nav>
      </header>

      <section class="hero">
        <p class="eyebrow">DEVELOPER · BUILDER · AI EXPLORER</p>

        <h1>
          A builder in the AI-native era.
        </h1>

        <p class="intro">
          我关注软件工程、AI 应用、开发者工具，以及如何把想法做成真正可用的产品。
          这里会记录我的技术探索、项目复盘和长期成长。
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <p class="eyebrow">WRITING SYSTEM</p>
        <h2>Notes on engineering, AI, and building.</h2>

        <div class="cards">
          <a class="card" href="/writing/">
            <p class="card-label">LONG-FORM</p>
            <h3>深度文章</h3>
            <p>
              沉淀相对完整的技术理解、工程经验、AI 应用思考和阶段性复盘。
            </p>
          </a>

          <a class="card" href="/logs/">
            <p class="card-label">DAILY LOGS</p>
            <h3>学习日志</h3>
            <p>
              记录每天学了什么、哪里掌握得不好、遇到了什么问题，以及下一步如何改进。
            </p>
          </a>

          <a class="card" href="/projects/">
            <p class="card-label">PROJECTS</p>
            <h3>项目复盘</h3>
            <p>
              不只展示结果，也记录项目背景、技术取舍、踩坑过程和后续计划。
            </p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  :global(*) {
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  :global(body) {
    margin: 0;
    min-height: 100vh;
    color: #eef3ff;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 88% 12%, rgba(92, 48, 160, 0.36), transparent 34%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 8% 8%, rgba(24, 82, 140, 0.26), transparent 32%),
      #080d1d;
    font-family:
      Inter,
      ui-sans-serif,
      system-ui,
      -apple-system,
      BlinkMacSystemFont,
      "Segoe UI",
      sans-serif;
  }

  .site {
    max-width: 1160px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 52px 28px 96px;
  }

  .nav {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .brand {
    color: #dbe6ff;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }

  nav {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  nav a {
    color: #b9c5dc;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  nav a:hover,
  .brand:hover {
    color: #9cc9ff;
  }

  .hero {
    padding: 130px 0 120px;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    margin: 0 0 28px;
    color: #8fc7ff;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
  }

  h1 {
    max-width: 820px;
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(58px, 9vw, 112px);
    line-height: 0.96;
    letter-spacing: -0.075em;
  }

  .intro {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin-top: 36px;
    color: #c4ccdc;
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.85;
  }

  .section {
    margin-top: 16px;
  }

  h2 {
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 0 0 34px;
    font-size: clamp(34px, 5vw, 52px);
    line-height: 1.08;
    letter-spacing: -0.055em;
  }

  .cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .card {
    display: block;
    min-height: 210px;
    padding: 28px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(166, 196, 255, 0.18);
    border-radius: 22px;
    background: rgba(12, 20, 40, 0.72);
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition:
      transform 180ms ease,
      border-color 180ms ease,
      background 180ms ease;
  }

  .card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: rgba(156, 201, 255, 0.5);
    background: rgba(18, 30, 58, 0.82);
  }

  .card-label {
    margin: 0 0 14px;
    color: #9cc9ff;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
  }

  .card h3 {
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    font-size: 25px;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
  }

  .card p:last-child {
    margin: 0;
    color: #c4ccdc;
    line-height: 1.85;
  }

  @media (max-width: 780px) {
    .site {
      padding: 32px 20px 72px;
    }

    .nav {
      align-items: flex-start;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 90px 0 82px;
    }

    .cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
